game.name: Emily’s Home Sweet Home
game.description:
Emily and Patrick want to rebuild their new house with a desire of making it a residential place of their dreams. In Emily?Home Sweet Home, you have to help your most favorite family repair and build up their dream home before it is too late. You will surely enjoy preparing various latest customized menus and extra daily challenges in this fast-paced time management free online game. Do not forget to decorate your home by unlocking all the achievements you made during the gameplay.?

Emily Home Sweet Home is an easy continuation of the most recognized and very challenging delicious franchise which describes the further story of Emily who is known to be a famous restaurant owner and is striving hard to build the life of her dreams. Have great time management fun while playing this cool flash game for many hours! One of the latest cooking games for girls, Emily Home Sweet Home will help you to learn how to serve your customers with their food needs before their patience runs out.?

You will receive a tip from your customers once you succeed in serving their food timely. Your overall performance will help to obtain a score at the end of each level in these 60-levels girls cooking games. The money you obtain from your customers will help to upgrade your restaurant with the latest possible features in order to perform better in future. The more food you will be able to serve, the higher money you will be able to earn through which you can renovate Emily dream house in the optimum possible way. Take your orders timely, cook the food properly and try to serve as quickly as you can to make your customers feel happy in this 3D cooking game.
